Marimo apps for analyzing ORCA calculations
===========================================

Installation
------------

```bash
uv tool install morca
```

Usage
-----

`morca` currently only supplies the `orbitals` app.

```bash
orbitals casscf.out
```

or simply

```bash
orbitals
```
